Source: disco
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Flip Hess <flip@offline-lab.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12), golang-go (>= 1.21), gcc, libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://github.com/offline-lab/disco
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/offline-lab/disco
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/offline-lab/disco.git

Package: disco-daemon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, disco-common
Recommends: disco-cli
Description: Lightweight name service daemon for airgapped networks
 Disco provides automatic service discovery and name resolution across
 nodes in an offline network without requiring external DNS services.
 .
 This package contains the main daemon that handles discovery, broadcast,
 service detection, and name resolution via a Unix domain socket.

Package: disco-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, disco-common
Description: Unified CLI for Disco daemon management
 Command-line interface for managing and querying the Disco daemon.
 Provides commands for host discovery, service management, key
 management, time synchronization, and network diagnostics.
 .
 All functionality is unified into a single 'disco' command.

Package: disco-gps-broadcaster
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GPS time broadcaster for Disco time synchronization
 Broadcasts GPS time via UDP for time synchronization in airgapped
 networks. Required when using the optional time_sync feature in
 disco-daemon.
 .
 Can also be implemented on Arduino or ESP32 devices.

Package: disco-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Common files for Disco packages
 Shared configuration, documentation, and NSS module for Disco.
 This package is automatically installed as a dependency of
 disco-daemon and disco-cli.
 .
 Includes the NSS module (libnss_disco.so.2) for native Linux
 name resolution integration.

Package: disco
Architecture: all
Depends: disco-daemon (= ${binary:Version}), disco-cli (= ${binary:Version}), disco-common (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Disco name service suite (metapackage)
 Metapackage that installs all Disco components:
 .
   * disco-daemon - Main discovery and name service daemon
   * disco-cli - Unified command-line interface
   * disco-common - Shared files and NSS module
   * disco-gps-broadcaster - GPS time broadcaster
 .
 This is the recommended package for full installations.
